snippet.title: Lets Play Army Men 1 Part 1
snippet.description:
We interrupt our currently planned schedule to bring more games from childhood...and fail...frustrating fail...enjoy!

Welcome to my Army Men 1, 2, and Toys In Space Lets Play Series, Army Men is by 3DO, and most everyone watching this should know of plastic toy soldiers atleast. 
Playing let alone recording these on Windows 7 is difficult, as these were made back for Windows 95/98, and no real support since Windows XP, since the lost of 3DO, but hopefully it all records well enough, and you all enjoy my failures at this series from my childhood.
